reviewText: Thanks for delivery of these DVDs.  God is still in the business of the supernatural.  Still a little conflicted about the gold teeth, gold dust and gems, but the other demonstrations of healing, believers loving and reaching out to the lost and the reality of God speaking and directing  believers - very inspiring.
Darren Wilson is writing,producing and directing some amazing videos. They will rock your world!
This series is a great challenge to those who think they have G-D all figured out.  It is vital at this time to know that "Aslan is not a tame lion but he is good!"

Amazing!  An experience I will never forget.  There's more to a Christian's life than just going to church.....that's for sure!  This has definitely been a life changing experience for me.  Since purchasing these, I have watched two times already and will watch again.
